item.title: Week 7
item.description:
Week 7: The “Ground Game”

For the first time since early August, FiveThirtyEight’s predicted winner for the 2024 presidential election has changed. After nearly three months of a slight lead for the Harris campaign in the site’s simulation counters, this weekend’s simulations pointed to a slightly higher likelihood for the Trump campaign, with the Republican nominee winning 52 times out of 100.
